00:37:41.662 --> 00:37:42.472
Thank you.

619
00:37:42.472 --> 00:37:42.761
Thank you.

620
00:37:49.462 --> 00:37:51.262
So our next speaker is Neil O'Brien.

621
00:37:51.362 --> 00:37:55.182
He's from UCLA, and his lab plays a leading role

622
00:37:55.282 --> 00:37:58.502
in research focused both on small molecule as well as

623
00:37:58.562 --> 00:38:01.382
antibody-based therapies in oncology.

